summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Chapter 23.32 of the Seattle Municipal Code at page 25 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone property located at 200 North 85th Street from Lowrise 1 Residential/Commercial (L1/RC) to Neighborhood Commercial 2 with a 65 foot height limit (NC2-65), and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition by Michael Whalen, C.F. 309054, DPD Project 3007932)
note: Originally referred 6/8/09. Re-referred to committee on 9/8/09.
